\par }{\f1\fs22 If you wish the encrypted reply to 
go to a newsgroup, then place the name of the newsgroup in the text box provided, plus the news service.  All you then need do is go to the newsgroup, say alt.anonymous.messages, or anything else you want to use, and then download your mail     }{\fs20  

